                                                style="object-fit: cover;">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-lg-6 pb-3">
                                        <p class="about-two__text-1 line_clamp">Kantaji Temple is a late-medieval Hindu
                                            temple at Kantanagar,
                                            Dinajpur.
                                            This temple is one of the
                                            best examples of the 18 th  century’s stunning religious edifices. It belongs to
                                            Hindu God
                                            Krishna
                                            and so
                                            it’s most popular among the devotees of Krishna in Bengal. Maharaja Pran Nath
                                            built this
                                            magnificent
                                            temple and devoted it to Krishna and his wife Rukmini. The construction work of
                                            this beautiful
                                            structure started in 1704 CE and was completed in 1722 CE. Its wall surfaces,
                                            both inside and
                                            outside
                                            are ornamented with figured and floral terracotta art. The stories from
                                            Mahabharata and
                                            Ramayana,
                                            the exploits of Krish,na and a series of absolutely fascinating contemporary
                                            social scenes are
                                            depicted on the wall through terracotta art. </p>
                                        <label for="read-more-checkbox" class="read-more__label"
                                            data-read-more="Read more" data-read-less="See less"
                                            aria-hidden="true"></label>
